{"tid":2303294,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"白色珍珠我屌你老母臭閪","createTime":"2020-11-27T20:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T17:01:29.000Z","uid":370510,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7368e774c2c5dfd1cf20190b0bc36faae02393e6","tid":2303294,"uid":370510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T20:56:33.000Z","msg":"呢樣嘢真係煩撚過閪<br />\n中學扁桃線發過炎之後就keep住有白色珍珠<br />\nDLLM搞到我中學唔撚敢面對面同人講嘢<br />\n已經日日用黑頭針整，點解仲一直出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩呢年日日戴口罩先唔會比人聞到我有呢樣嘢<br />\n好想切咗扁桃線佢，但又成幾萬蚊<br />\n點解我係窮撚呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好笑係我又無喉嚨痛喎<br />\n淨係日日出白色珍珠，跟本玩鳩我<br />\n你究竟幾時先肯走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登第一個Po就要屌你老母臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53cfbf404e2e04ae910490fdb9557d2f0f3aef75","tid":2303294,"uid":16528,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T20:57:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c0206bee5abbf5c1b2709238fdfee5ed5774248","tid":2303294,"uid":65818,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T21:02:11.000Z","msg":"做尖游水<br />\n重訓同帶氧都做<br />\n鼻塞鼻水倒流冇咗自然冇事<br />\n<br />\n利申：鼻敏感加白珍 完全康復<br />\n<br />\n不過一唔做兩個星期又會有返"},{"pid":"a2839d3e51a416c615c7f69e3cf0b1a7ad2be01f","tid":2303294,"uid":370510,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"53cfbf404e2e04ae910490fdb9557d2f0f3aef75","tid":2303294,"uid":16528,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T20:57:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T21:03:28.000Z","msg":"個陣以為飲得少水<br />\n之後日日返學飲三支水都係咁<br />